cs.CR, cs.SE, cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.PL

This paper deals with vulnerability management systems and software analysis, which are related to computer security (cs.CR). It also involves the use of dictionaries and feeds, which are common in software engineering (cs.SE). The paper proposes a method for recommending CPE identifiers, which involves data analysis and prioritization, making it relevant to information systems (cs.SI) and cyber security (cs.CY). Finally, the paper discusses the implementation of a VMS, which involves programming languages and software development (cs.PL).
